              <span id="reviewTextContainer2262263483" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17286183966320832877">This realistic fiction book follows the life of a teenaged girl as she deals with the struggles of growing up. You would like this book if you like coming of age stories. The theme of A Ring of Endless Light is that life, though hard at times, is easier when family is there to help. </span>

          </span>
